{
  "stem": "210.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the snow-- you had to stay barefoot in the snow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have to stand like this-- you know, this far apart from each other because so there wouldn't be-- you couldn't get warm from another body.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they counted us, and we would stay there for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we would have to go and wash, you know, in the cold water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we would go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And about that time already, we had to like keep our barracks-- you know, we had to wash the floors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have to go for the soup, you know, and things like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by that time, after two months, there was so many people started dying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everybody-- typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- you know, and I got sick too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was on the third-- on the third thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at that time, they brought us a little piece of bread, you know, and a little water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you couldn't go down, you didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we were just laying there and, you know, and then after a while, one of the girls died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They came in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They looked what's going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of the girls died and they just pushed her down, you know, like-- and when she fell down it made such a tug, you now?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next night, another one died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The third night, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was so sick and I had such a high temperature.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My lips were burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just, you know, I couldn't feel anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- when they threw the third girl down, I somehow said to myself, I don't want to be thrown down like this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to go down.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
